1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 2=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(The Army Blasts the Adulterous Couple)

4
00:00:53,390 --> 00:00:55,240
I invited you all here today

5
00:00:55,470 --> 00:00:56,880
to discuss someone.

6
00:00:57,430 --> 00:00:58,470
Pan Yang.

7
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,370
He'll soon enter the imperial court
and be granted a noble title.

8
00:01:02,430 --> 00:01:05,480
But I believe his character
is deeply flawed.

9
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:06,430
He's ungrateful

10
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:08,990
and I don't want him gaining a foothold
in the imperial court.

11
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:10,870
We owe everything we have today

12
00:01:10,870 --> 00:01:11,870
to you, Tower Master.

13
00:01:12,150 --> 00:01:13,510
Please give us your orders.

14
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:16,760
Each of your six ministries should
find a reasonable justification

15
00:01:17,350 --> 00:01:18,870
to keep him out.

16
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:20,200
Understood?

17
00:01:21,070 --> 00:01:21,590
Understood.

18
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:23,710
According to my investigation,

19
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:26,430
Pan Yang's military expenditures
during the northern campaign

20
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:28,560
far exceeded those of units
with the same organization.

21
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:30,350
His accounts are vague and inconsistent.

22
00:01:30,590 --> 00:01:32,400
He is unfit to join
the Ministry of Revenue.

23
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:35,230
I've heard Pan Yang

24
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:37,840
planned to cast aside his lawful wife
the moment he returned home.

25
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:39,560
His personal conduct is disgraceful.

26
00:01:39,670 --> 00:01:41,590
He is unfit to join
the Ministry of Personnel.

27
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,070
Exactly.

28
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,840
Pan Yang is obsessed with winning glory.

29
00:01:45,150 --> 00:01:47,550
I heard he recklessly charged ahead
several times in battle,

30
00:01:47,590 --> 00:01:50,040
and only managed to win
because his men risked their lives.

31
00:01:50,050 --> 00:01:51,580
He's nothing more than a reckless brute.

32
00:01:51,590 --> 00:01:53,200
He is unfit to join the Ministry of War.

33
00:01:53,950 --> 00:01:54,790
Makes perfect sense.

34
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:56,980
I think everything you've said
is perfectly reasonable.

35
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,300
Ministry of Rites, Ministry of Justice,
and Ministry of Works.

36
00:01:58,430 --> 00:01:59,280
Let's hear your views.

37
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,600
I heard Pan Yang returned home today

38
00:02:01,610 --> 00:02:03,710
and allowed his concubine
to insult his lawful wife.

39
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:05,000
He has no regard for rank,

40
00:02:05,010 --> 00:02:06,400
and turns proper order upside down.

41
00:02:06,410 --> 00:02:07,940
How could someone like that
serve as an official?

42
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:09,910
The Ministry of Rites
will never accept him.

43
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,790
If he wants to join
the Ministry of Justice,

44
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,280
we should first investigate

45
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:15,590
whether his military achievements
were falsely claimed.

46
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:20,120
Well...

47
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,750
Judging by Pan Yang,

48
00:02:23,910 --> 00:02:25,190
he's short in stature

49
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:28,310
and even walks awkwardly.

50
00:02:29,190 --> 00:02:31,470
A clumsy good for nothing like him

51
00:02:31,810 --> 00:02:33,360
has no place in the Ministry of Works.

52
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,240
Good.

53
00:02:35,750 --> 00:02:38,240
I think every one of you
has made an excellent point.

54
00:02:38,590 --> 00:02:40,000
So, by the sound of it,

55
00:02:40,190 --> 00:02:43,000
Pan Yang is utterly worthless

56
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:45,190
from head to toe.

57
00:02:46,150 --> 00:02:47,790
- Rest assured, Tower Master.
- Rest assured, Tower Master.

58
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:51,000
We'll make sure
every door is closed to him.

59
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:54,870
Good.

60
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:57,870
I'm very pleased with today's meeting.

61
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,470
A complete success.

62
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:00,910
Meeting adjourned.

63
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,390
- We'll take our leave.
- We'll take our leave.

64
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:10,080
Let's see how smug you can be now.

65
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:13,400
Tower Master,

66
00:03:13,470 --> 00:03:15,190
Pan Yang took Li Muyan, that mistress,

67
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:16,550
back to the Li Residence
for her return visit.

68
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,590
He even used your money

69
00:03:17,590 --> 00:03:19,240
to buy them a whole pile of gifts.

70
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:20,870
Seriously?

71
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:23,400
That scoundrel cheated on me,
and I let that slide.

72
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,790
Now he even
has the nerve to spend my silver?

73
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,080
I've had enough.

74
00:03:27,190 --> 00:03:28,310
I'm going to beat them both.

75
00:03:28,630 --> 00:03:30,520
Tower Master, you mean...

76
00:03:31,110 --> 00:03:32,590
I've decided to teach Pan Yang a lesson.

77
00:03:32,590 --> 00:03:33,670
We're attacking the Li Residence

78
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,680
and giving them a lesson
they'll never forget.

79
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:36,470
He needs to learn

80
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,310
what happens when he crosses me.

81
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:40,060
(Li Residence)

82
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,160
Thank you for understanding,
Mother-in-law,

83
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:45,590
and allowing Muyan
to join the Pan Residence.

84
00:03:46,290 --> 00:03:47,470
I'd like to offer you a toast.

85
00:03:47,690 --> 00:03:49,680
I'll be counting on your support
in the future.

86
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,470
Of course.

87
00:03:53,710 --> 00:03:56,560
Muyan is fortunate to have married you.

88
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:57,680
From now on,

89
00:03:57,870 --> 00:04:00,840
if you ever need money
to smooth things over in official circles,

90
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:01,960
just ask.

91
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:04,590
You're too generous, Mother-in-law.

92
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:08,360
As for Li Qingqing...

93
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,590
What's there to worry about?

94
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,240
She's just an illegitimate daughter.

95
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,680
What trouble could she possibly cause?

96
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,630
Exactly.

97
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:17,190
Since I know you have
no feelings for Li Qingqing,

98
00:04:17,510 --> 00:04:20,270
I can finally rest easy
and throw her out of the Li Residence.

99
00:04:20,270 --> 00:04:22,740
(Li Residence)

100
00:04:37,660 --> 00:04:38,980
(Li Residence)

101
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:49,780
Please don't be upset, Mother-in-law.

102
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,360
Let's not talk about

103
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:53,120
that wretched woman today.

104
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:54,920
Allow me to offer you another toast.

105
00:04:55,190 --> 00:04:55,830
Good.

106
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,240
Launch!

107
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,360
Hit them!

108
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:18,750
What's going on?

109
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,510
How dare you!

110
00:05:24,310 --> 00:05:27,040
I am the General
of the Northern Expedition Cavalry.

111
00:05:27,050 --> 00:05:28,940
How dare you attack
an official of the imperial court!

112
00:05:28,940 --> 00:05:29,780
(Li Residence)

113
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,630
I'm here to deal with you!

114
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:32,630
Launch!

115
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:38,900
Bring up the battering ram!

116
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:39,900
Break down the gate!

117
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:50,600
Has the Beicang army invaded?

118
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:53,510
I... I'm just a general.

119
00:05:53,510 --> 00:05:55,000
Why are they attacking me?

120
00:05:56,070 --> 00:05:58,630
Yang, what do we do now?

121
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,510
I don't know!

122
00:05:59,510 --> 00:06:01,070
Um... Pan Yang,

123
00:06:01,070 --> 00:06:02,480
they're after you.

124
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,190
Why don't

125
00:06:03,190 --> 00:06:05,120
you go out and face them?

126
00:06:06,270 --> 00:06:06,750
Ram it!

127
00:06:10,430 --> 00:06:11,750
Charge!

128
00:06:11,750 --> 00:06:13,270
- Kill!
- Kill!

129
00:06:16,270 --> 00:06:17,070
Your Highness.

130
00:06:18,510 --> 00:06:19,310
What is it?

131
00:06:19,420 --> 00:06:20,180
(Chang Lin, Zheng Yuanhe's
personal guard)

132
00:06:20,180 --> 00:06:22,090
An unidentified army
has appeared east of the city.

133
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,160
They're well trained

134
00:06:23,190 --> 00:06:25,070
and equipped with catapults
and battering rams.

135
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:25,830
They are...

136
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:27,790
They're attacking outside
the city or the palace?

137
00:06:28,550 --> 00:06:30,090
They're surrounding a private residence.

138
00:06:32,390 --> 00:06:33,390
A private residence?

139
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:36,870
Prepare my horse.

140
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,260
Yes, Your Highness.

141
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:44,920
- Kill!
- Kill!

142
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:52,870
You...

143
00:06:53,430 --> 00:06:54,510
Who are you people?

144
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:55,950
Men,

145
00:06:56,430 --> 00:06:57,830
tell General Pan

146
00:06:58,310 --> 00:07:00,000
what happens to anyone

147
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,510
who dares disrespect me.

148
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:02,800
- Yes!
- Yes!

149
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:07,120
- Kill!
- Kill!

150
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:21,630
Stop!

151
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:22,680
Stop!

152
00:07:25,950 --> 00:07:27,430
As for you...

153
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,160
No...

154
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:30,800
I never offended the Tower Master.

155
00:07:50,390 --> 00:07:51,070
That's enough.

156
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,310
Retreat.

157
00:08:18,530 --> 00:08:19,830
To mobilize an army of that scale

158
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:21,200
with siege weapons like those...

159
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,070
Your Highness,

160
00:08:23,870 --> 00:08:25,630
they were clearly
conducting a siege drill.

161
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:42,600
Good thing we pulled out in time.

162
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:44,080
We almost ran into
that scheming Crown Prince.

163
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,080
Don't worry, Tower Master.

164
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:47,260
The brothers have already made it
back to the workshop.

165
00:08:48,450 --> 00:08:50,830
We just caused quite a scene
and nearly ran into the authorities.

166
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:51,900
We need to calm our nerves.

167
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:52,840
Let's go!

168
00:08:53,290 --> 00:08:54,320
Tower Master, watch out!

169
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:05,320
General Pan,

170
00:09:05,550 --> 00:09:06,960
who dared lay a hand on you?

171
00:09:07,750 --> 00:09:08,270
They...

172
00:09:08,270 --> 00:09:10,360
There were over ten thousand of them.

173
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:12,720
They all wore masks,

174
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,390
and they pelted me with stones!

175
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:16,960
Wangshi Tower!

176
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:19,000
They were Wangshi Tower's
ghost soldiers!

177
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:20,280
They scared me to death!

178
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,390
Where are you going?

179
00:09:25,390 --> 00:09:26,360
Don't leave me!

180
00:09:31,550 --> 00:09:34,030
Your Highness, the people behind this
are from Wangshi Tower.

181
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:39,480
Right under the Son of Heaven's nose,

182
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:43,840
they've hidden such a well trained army.

183
00:09:44,630 --> 00:09:45,390
Tomorrow,

184
00:09:46,810 --> 00:09:48,360
go persuade Wangshi Tower to surrender.

185
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:49,130
Yes, Your Highness.

186
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:52,060
(Wangshi Tower)

187
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:01,360
(This scheming Crown Prince
is like a leech.)

188
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,630
(I just can't shake him off.)

189
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:08,150
What brings Your Highness here?

190
00:10:09,020 --> 00:10:11,390
The strategy for the imperial examinations
you gave me, Tower Master,

191
00:10:11,510 --> 00:10:13,550
has restored integrity
to Great Yong's officialdom.

192
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:16,870
This is a token of my appreciation
for you, Tower Master.

193
00:10:17,330 --> 00:10:18,910
(I only wanted
to use the imperial examinations)

194
00:10:18,910 --> 00:10:21,010
(to select diligent officials
who truly care for the people.)

195
00:10:21,150 --> 00:10:22,240
(But he used them as an excuse)

196
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,260
(to execute dozens of officials.)

197
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:24,870
(Who knows if he was really
eliminating political rivals?)

198
00:10:24,870 --> 00:10:26,270
(He's far too calculating.)

199
00:10:26,550 --> 00:10:29,120
Your Highness
has executed quite a few officials.

200
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:31,240
Aren't you worried the court historians

201
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,870
will call you an unjust ruler?

202
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:40,200
Meanwhile, Wangshi Tower
has become renowned far and wide.

203
00:10:40,210 --> 00:10:42,210
People from all sides
are eager to align themselves with it.

204
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,890
Why not establish Wangshi Tower
in the Eastern Palace?

205
00:10:44,910 --> 00:10:46,360
I can ensure Wangshi Tower

206
00:10:46,370 --> 00:10:48,270
will never be suspected
by the imperial court.

207
00:10:48,500 --> 00:10:50,250
(He's trying
to bring me under his control.)

208
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:52,270
(And keep me
where he can keep an eye on me.)

209
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:53,180
(In his dreams.)

210
00:10:53,310 --> 00:10:56,200
We've only met twice, yet Your Highness
already speaks to me so candidly.

211
00:10:58,030 --> 00:10:58,750
Unfortunately,

212
00:10:59,270 --> 00:11:01,000
I'm nothing more
than a carefree wanderer.

213
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,870
I have no interest in court affairs.

214
00:11:07,750 --> 00:11:10,910
Tower Master, I hope you'll reconsider.

215
00:11:17,010 --> 00:11:20,400
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

216
00:11:21,160 --> 00:11:24,540
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

217
00:11:25,310 --> 00:11:27,050
♪Your smile♪

218
00:11:27,310 --> 00:11:29,600
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

219
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:33,280
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

220
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:37,050
♪Yet I stand before you♪

221
00:11:37,790 --> 00:11:41,620
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

222
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:43,960
♪Though fate tries♪

223
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:46,540
♪To make us pass each other by♪

224
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:50,180
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

225
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:52,070
♪Though time slips by♪

226
00:11:52,070 --> 00:11:53,830
♪As day turns into night♪

227
00:11:54,350 --> 00:11:58,370
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

228
00:11:58,790 --> 00:12:01,170
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

229
00:12:01,170 --> 00:12:02,960
♪Blessed by fate♪

230
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:08,120
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

231
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:10,560
♪Your smiling face♪

232
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:13,400
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

233
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:17,020
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

234
00:12:17,540 --> 00:12:21,000
♪And wander the world together♪

235
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,340
♪Holding you close♪

236
00:12:22,340 --> 00:12:24,880
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

237
00:12:24,880 --> 00:12:27,200
♪Your tenderness♪

238
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:30,060
♪Is the brightest moon♪

239
00:12:30,060 --> 00:12:33,760
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

240
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:37,570
♪Our love will never fade away♪

241
00:12:37,570 --> 00:12:40,030
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

242
00:12:40,560 --> 00:12:44,810
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

243
00:12:54,290 --> 00:12:56,450
♪Your smiling face♪

244
00:12:56,630 --> 00:12:59,240
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

245
